{"type": "article", "id": 35362, "title": "奥特曼推出保存版BOX，以及，Converse的东京支线很酷啊 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-12-08T02:40:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 306, "name": "奥特曼"}, {"id": 7332, "name": "KFC"}, {"id": 7776, "name": "NikeLab"}, {"id": 22806, "name": "Herschel"}, {"id": 35616, "name": "Converse Tokyo"}, {"id": 14370, "name": "reebok"}, {"id": 32840, "name": "Honest"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161208102015zZl3hvPEkjHbsJcT.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2016/focus/athletic-outdoor/reebok-moves-headquarters-to-boston-283501/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Reebok 的总部要搬迁</b></a> | Reebok 要离开现在位于马萨诸塞州 Canton 的总部，计划在 2017 年秋季之前，搬迁至波士顿的 Seaport 区。Reebok 的新总部大楼共有五层，占地超 220000 平方英尺，约 20438 平方米。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/job-cuts-jessica-albas-honest-co-could-mean-deal-ipo-are-tabled-10720829/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>明星创业公司 Honest 计划裁员</b></a> | 好莱坞明星 Jessica Alba 的公司 Honest 计划裁员 80 人，这占据了员工总数的近 14%。这次裁员的同时 Honest 还将重新调整公司的业务方向，这似乎意味着 Honest 在近一段时间内，不太可能出售或是进行 IPO 上市了。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/converse-tokyo-2017-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">Converse 日本支线 Converse Tokyo</a>，发布了第三季的全新造型特辑，本季主打整洁感和流畅的线条，继续以今年大热的阔腿高腰裤为重点，该系列计划于明年 1 月在全日本上市。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081013114dRkbWTjlu2MF5ZU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208101311TRkE7jcuzvqpgMCO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208101311W5kbVLHo9dEXBsxR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208101311dXzIHoPUGuSBbQKx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081013115gLZVis7D0UuoKdE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208101311EuplXTjx4KUzMrd6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208101321qjbcdZ3vwPlEgiU0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208101321bXhzE1WluRnNfidG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">已有五十多年历史的日本国民动画《奥特曼》，将在今天推出<a href=\"https://ultraman-tre.shop-pro.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">保存版纪念 BOX Ultraman Treasures</a>。该纪念版包括 180 页的书籍以及超过 500 张全彩写真，售价为税后 18360 日元，可在官网订购。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081013296uYr3lpgib0mUBPR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208101336Gk0bJQWaVIB9NO8s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/kfc-scented-candle\" rel=\"nofollow\">KFC 推出圣诞限量版香氛蜡烛</a>，特别将 11 种草药和香料混合，制成这款蜡烛。不过，它并不会公开发售，只会在新泽西地区作为社交媒体活动的礼物送出。呃，暂时想象不出来是什么味儿的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208102130UXFVc7uqmwhYLxZO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Givenchy 的创意总监<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/rt-x-nikelab-air-zoom-legend\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Riccardo Tisci 与 NikeLab 联合打造的 Air Zoom Legend 在今天正式开售</a>。这双鞋的高筒鞋身来自经典的  Chelsea 靴款，凸起的橡胶后跟还挺有未来感的。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208101354cnvHeWKlmbIxRwko.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081013545sMxNPLh4GSvOJTE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208101401u9TX0UlrQAkEJv6o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208101401s8cnEJhd6gXylK9G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208101407pvofaH2CkRi8cV6Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">除了户外防水的 TRAIL 系列外，Herschel Supply Co. 的 SURPLUS 系列也同样精彩。本季的新品中，采用了独特的蓝染技术，加之耐磨的斜纹布料，尽显美式复古风格。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081020340nbVEHlsCBwz8a5p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208102034z1ZuqpMrYKyHnes6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208102034bVne850FEDPTfaYv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208102035YHFUEaXpTbZDit8B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208102036giMVumfj4TLBK0Yc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208102037Y9tKhn8wxz3R6WiA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208102037MjXmL1aJr2FiZNHx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612081020377dLVKk6FChZ9xPOA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161208102037jynJ0K8mRGu6932k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}